clobbering machine
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:the local or bureaucratic conservatism allegedly responsible for quashing individual creativity.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:-
Pronunciation:
Notes: often preceded by (great) Kiwi/New Zealand
